  "texts": [
    "If a forget gate outputs 1 (one), the information is stored in the cell state.",
    "The sigmoid function creates a vector in the following step.",
    "New possible values are stored in this vector.",
    "The updated values are specified by input gates, and the vector C 0 t is updated with possible new values.",
    "This new vector is evaluated with the following formulas;i t ¼ rðW i ½h tÀ1; x t þ b i Þ C 0 t ¼ tanhðW c ½h tÀ1; x t þ b c Þ Now cell's old state C tÀ1 is updated to new cell state C t. C t ¼ f t Ã C tÀ1 þ i t Ã C 0 tEventually, we select the network's output regarding on the cell state."
